jebcarter/psyonic-cetacean-20B.name: jebcarter/psyonic-cetacean-20B
jebcarter/psyonic-cetacean-20B.description: Older but extremely creative model that does well across a wide range of tasks but has some drawbacks. extremely high KV context size, being near 6gb per 4k context, and below average intelegence compared to modern models that will use the same memory. Great option for 16-24gb cards. Strongest when doing story/adventure but still great at KoboldAI flagship model. Excels across a wide variety of tasks, Very verbose and suitable for storytelling and RP. a Variant exists TiefighterLR-13b that may be better for Adventure mode. Alpaca RP focused model that excels across many tasks. Generally fairly reliable even outside of RP.
